        <item>
          <title>Apple Stops Offering Advanced Data Security in UK Amid Government Demand</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Tech giant Apple has stopped offering an advanced data security option for British users after the government reportedly demanded that the company provide backdoor access for any data those users have stored in the cloud.]]></description>
